    h1 Privacy Policy
    p.last-updated Last Updated: January 2025

    p Welcome to StoryLives! This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, protect, and handle your information when you use our mobile application.

    h2 1. Information We Collect
    h3 1.1 Information You Provide
    ul
      li Account Information: Email address, username, and profile information
      li Premium Subscription Details: Payment information is handled securely through Google Play Billing
      li User Content: Preferences, saved stories, and interaction history
      li Communication: Customer support messages and feedback

    h3 1.2 Automatically Collected Information
    ul
      li Device Information: Device type, operating system, unique device identifiers
      li Usage Data: App features used, reading history, interaction patterns
      li Performance Data: App performance metrics and error logs
      li Location Data: General location (country/region) for content personalization

    h2 2. How We Use Your Information
    ul
      li Provide and maintain our services
      li Process your premium subscription
      li Personalize your content experience
      li Improve and optimize our application
      li Communicate updates and recommendations
      li Provide customer support
      li Ensure compliance with our terms of service

    h2 3. Premium Subscriptions
    p StoryLives offers premium features through subscription plans. When you purchase a subscription:
    ul
      li Payment processing is handled securely by Google Play Billing
      li Subscription status and purchase history are stored securely
      li You can manage subscriptions through Google Play Store
      li Cancellation and refund policies follow Google Play Store guidelines

